				<div class="lead-img" id="lead-img">
												
					
						<a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/christian-bale-out-slammer-onto-s33021/photos/" ><img src="http://buzznet-43.vo.llnwd.net/cb/assets/imgx/2/7/7/4/6/9/1/orig-2774691.jpg" border="0" alt="Christian Bale: Out of the Slammer, Onto the Red Carpet" title="Christian Bale: Out of the Slammer, Onto the Red Carpet" oncontextmenu="return false" /></a>			
						
									</div>
				<div class="media-source">Source: <a target="_partner" href='http://www.gettyimages.com/' target='_blank'>Getty Images</a></div>								<h2 style="width: 570px;">Batman makes his first post-jail appearance.</h2>
				<div class="post-logo"><a href="http://xoxojaniepie.celebuzz.com/user/"><img src="http://buzznet-05.vo.llnwd.net/cb/assets/feed_icons/cb_storyicon_32.gif" border="0" alt="Celebuzz" /></a></div>
				<div class="post-subline">
					<span class="post-time">Posted on 07/24/2008 10:40 AM</span> 
										<span class="post-byline">by <a href="http://celebuzz.celebuzz.com/user/" rel="nofollow">Celebuzz</a></span>
				</div>
				<div class="story-body story-body-new" id="story-main-body">
					<p><strong>Christian Bale</strong> put on a rueful grin and walked the red carpet for the Barcelona premiere of his <a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/batman-kicked-spidermans-ass-s31971/" target="_blank">blockbuster summer flick</a>, <em>The Dark Knight</em>, on Wednesday.</p>
<p>It was just one day after <a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/busted-christian-bale-goes-bat-s32411/" target="_blank">his arrest</a> in London on Tuesday after he reportedly unleashed hell on his family at the Dorchester Hotel.&#160; His mom <strong>Jenny Bale</strong> was said to have made <a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/christian-bale-was-caught-family-s32731/" target="_blank">some unkind remarks about his wife</a>, <strong>Sandra Sibi Blazic</strong> (pictured here with the hotheaded star).</p>
<p>Bale posed for pics and signed autographs outside the Coliseum Theater last night, but he didn't answer reporters' questions about the arrest.</p>
<p>He called the incident a "deeply personal matter" and requested that the press would "respect my privacy."</p>
<p>Good luck with that. You're Batman! People want to know why you treated your family like you would some <a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/heath-ledger-oscar-goes-toheaven-s25791/" target="_blank">Gotham City supervillain</a>.</p>				</div>
									<div class="next-story"><a href="http://www.celebuzz.com/nick-jonas-selena-gomez-tween-s33031/"><b>Next:</b> Nick Jonas and Selena Gomez: Tween Stars in Love? &raquo;</a></div>
							</div>
			
		
		</div><!-- end .story-listing -->
		
		
