			<p><span>Because he has a movie to promote, Christian Bale can't lay low in the midst of his whole assault arrest/family drama and was seen out in public. It's probably a small consolation to him that his movie is kicking ass at the box office.<br />
<br />
I'm quite impressed with how well he and his wife Sandra "Sibi" Blazic are keeping it together here at The Dark Knight premiere in Barcelona, Spain. But then again, Christian's a good actor. He probably just decided to take on the role of a man whose family isn't driving him up the wall. He's that good.</span></p>
